<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>240</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Migilo hungin, A hun sam hi,
 Isu keng bul ah;
 Hungin, lunghei in, na puok chu nga'n,
 Isu keng bul ah!

[V2]
 Aw hung nga'n la, hungnga'n la,
 Na lunggil gikpuok nga'n la;
 Aw hung nga'n la, hung nga'n la,
 Isu keng bul ah.

[V3]
 2. Hungin, gingin na chawlh nang hawlin,
 Isu keng bul ah;
 Na lungthim gikpuok chu hung nga'n la,
 Isu keng bul ah.

[V4]
 3. Hungin, ginna'n a hun hihdam thei,
 Isu keng bul ah;
 Aw, na thagau chau chu hun pui in,
 Isu keng bul ah!

[V5]
 4. Hungin, Lalpa pakin mun a um,
 Isu keng bul ah;
 Na gitloh gikpuok cheng chu nga'n la,
 Isu keng bul ah.</lyrics>
<title>LAY IT DOWN</title>
</song>